text: Nathanaël Dieng (born 13 April 1997) is a French professional footballer who plays as defender for Rodez. ==Professional career== A youth product of Saint- Étienne, Dieng joined his hometown club Grenoble in 2014, and went on loan with Rodez AF in 2018. He made his professional debut with Rodez in a 2–0 Ligue 2 win over AJ Auxerre on 26 July 2019. ==Personal life== Dieng is the younger brother of the footballer Timothée Dieng.
